2001-03-13 Hiroshi Takekawa <sian@fennel.org>

	* src/multiskkserv.c: Implemented -r(chroot) and -f(family). Use
	snprintf() instead of sprintf(). Now listen() only AF_INET or
	AF_INET6. More error reporting. Cosmetic changes.

